(115, 1, '2016-06-06 09:42:33', '2016-06-06 07:42:33', 'For the first time ever in a mechanical watch, the <strong>ZEITWERK MINUTE REPEATER</strong> brings together a jumping numerals display with a decimal minute repeater. The acoustic time indication consists of a low-pitched tone for each elapsed hour, a double tone for each elapsed ten-minute period, and a high-pitched tone for each elapsed minute. Thus, the time as sounded corresponds exactly to the time as displayed.', 'Zeitwerk Minute Repeater', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'zeitwerk-minute-repeater', '', '', '2016-06-06 09:47:34', '2016-06-06 07:47:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/eshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=115', 0, 'product', '', 0),
